page.title: 09STUART PETHICK'S DAY (2)
page.content: 12.30 Went out to play. 1.00 Came in.Played educational games. 2.15 Went out to play. 2.30 Had swimming lesson.If the weather is too cold he is not allowed to go. 3.15 He caught a yellow minibus home. 3.23 When he gets home he got changed out of school uniform.Then he played football with his brother.Then he played tennis. 6.10 Went in and had tea. He had fish fingers,chips and orange squash. Afterwards he watched Television. 8.00 He played noughts and crosses with his dad. 9.30 Went to bed and read a book. 9.50 Went to sleep.
